# Token Cost Advice Request (extension/OpenClaw)
# Purpose: assemble bounded token/cost usage facts and enqueue an advisory
# request for a Cursor-side agent via `agent.send_task`. This example is
# advisory-only and does not perform any remediation itself.

S core agent

L0: R core now ->ts J L1

L1: X payload {
  "date": "2026-03-09",
  "total_cost_usd": 12.34,
  "daily_limit_usd": 20.0,
  "total_tokens": 450000,
  "prompt_tokens": 300000,
  "completion_tokens": 150000,
  "top_models": ["gpt-4.1-mini", "gpt-4.1", "claude-3.5-sonnet"]
} J L2

L2: X task {
  "schema_version": "1.0",
  "task_id": "token-cost-advice-20260309",
  "requester_id": "openclaw.token_cost_tracker",
  "target_agent": "cursor.advisor",
  "target_role": "advisor",
  "task_type": "advisory_token_cost_review",
  "description": "Review daily token cost and suggest safe model/usage optimizations.",
  "input": {
    "refs": [],
    "payload": payload
  },
  "allowed_tools": ["http", "fs.read-only"],
  "approval_required": "none",
  "callback": {
    "file_append": "agents/openclaw.token_cost_tracker/results.jsonl"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "ainl.program_id": "token_cost_advice_request.v1"
  }
} J L3

L3: R agent send_task task ->task_id J task_id

